类 IndentingPrintWriter

    java.io.Closeable, java.io.Flushable, java.lang.Appendable, java.lang.AutoCloseable

    public class IndentingPrintWriter
extends java.io.PrintWriter
    Lightweight wrapper around PrintWriter that automatically indents newlines based on internal state. It also automatically wraps long lines based on given line length.

    Delays writing indent until first actual write on a newline, enabling indent modification after newline.
